      "comment": "LITTLE BLUE OPAL (1) is a solid beginner and with a good start can clear the draw. Last start finished 7th over 401m at this track beaten 6 lengths (23.53) behind Smart Aussie in a Grade 5 on April 24. Rates on top and should go close. ELLA'S GLORY (5) turned in a moderate performance last time when sixth at The Gardens over 515m behind Soft Whisper (30.31) in a Grade 5. Cannot be taken lightly. WELL READ (8) was safely held last time out, finishing sixth at this track over 520m behind Hey Arnold (30.95) in a Mix. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Should be thereabouts. WHERE'S HARRY (2) should bounce back after an unplaced effort here recently.",
